---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About | Pejji" description="We exist because Nigerian businesses deserve better than template sites. Meet the Pejji team.">

  <!-- HEADER -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold reveal">Meet Pejji</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-subtle text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto reveal" style="transition-delay: 100ms;">We exist because Nigerian businesses deserve better than template sites.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- OUR STORY -->
  <section class="pb-16 sm:pb-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-8 reveal">Our Story</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6 text-subtle leading-relaxed reveal" style="transition-delay: 100ms;">
        <p>
          We started Pejji because we saw a gap that nobody was filling properly. Millions of Nigerian businesses (restaurants, fashion brands, logistics companies, beauty salons) were either stuck without a website or paying too much for mediocre templates that didn't convert.
        </p>
        <p>
          The big agencies charge millions and take months. The freelancers are unreliable. The template builders look generic. Nigerian SME owners deserve a third option: professional, custom-built websites at honest prices, delivered fast, with real human support.
        </p>
        <p>
          That's what Pejji is. We build websites that actually work for your business: fast-loading, mobile-first, security-audited, and designed to convert visitors into customers. Every single one.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm">
          Part of <a href="#" class="text-teal hover:underline">BlessedOps Group</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VALUES -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-surface/50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 sm:mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold">What We Stand For</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 lg:gap-8 stagger-children">
        <div class="card-tactile bg-surface border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-teal/20">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Speed</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-subtle leading-relaxed">Your site shouldn't take months. Card tier ships in 48 hours. Even our most complex builds launch within 3 weeks.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-tactile bg-surface border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-teal/20">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Security</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-subtle leading-relaxed">Every site is security-audited before launch. We don't just build pretty, we build safe. Your customers' data stays protected.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-tactile bg-surface border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-teal/20">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 5a1 1 0 011-1h14a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V5zM4 13a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Simplicity</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-subtle leading-relaxed">No jargon, no complexity. Just a site that works. You send us content on WhatsApp, we build your website. That simple.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-tactile bg-surface border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:border-teal/20">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Support</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-subtle leading-relaxed">Real humans on WhatsApp, not chatbots. We respond within 2 hours. Your questions never go unanswered.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TEAM -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 sm:mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold">The Team</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-subtle text-lg">Small team. Big results.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 stagger-children">
        {[
          { name: "Team Member", role: "Remote Lead", desc: "Strategy & Development", initials: "RL" },
          { name: "Team Member", role: "Ops Lead", desc: "Client Relations & Delivery", initials: "OL" },
          { name: "Team Member", role: "Technical Lead", desc: "Build & QA", initials: "TL" },
          { name: "Team Member", role: "Sales", desc: "Business Development", initials: "BD" },
        ].map((member) => (
          <div class="bg-surface border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center hover:border-teal/20 transition-colors">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto bg-teal/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
              <span class="text-teal text-xl font-bold">{member.initials}</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">{member.name}</h3>
            <p class="text-teal text-sm font-medium mt-1">{member.role}</p>
            <p class="text-subtle text-sm mt-2">{member.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-surface/50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold reveal">Let's build something great together.</h2>
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="https://wa.me/2348000000000?text=Hi%20Pejji!%20I'm%20interested%20in%20getting%20a%20website%20for%20my%20business." target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 bg-green-500 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-green-600 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/></svg>
          Chat on WhatsApp
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-orange text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-orange/90 transition-colors">
          Get Started
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Base>
